Trivia[]

Galio, the Sentinel's Sorrow
  • ▶️  "Two birds with one stone? Have you met my parents?" is a reference to the idiom 'kill two birds with one stone'.
Gatekeeper Galio (old)
  • ▶️  "Dead men tell no tales? I wish... they're never quiet" is a reference to the saying 'dead men tell no tales'.
Gatekeeper Galio
  • ▶️  "Hell is other champions." is a reference to the famous saying "Hell is other people" from the play "No Exit by Jean-Paul Sartre
Galio, the Colossus
  • ▶️  "I came to chew bubblegun and kick butt, and I'm all out of butt." is a reference to the 1988 film They Live in which the main character, enters a bank with a pump-action shotgun and says "I have come here to chew bubblegum and kick ass, and I'm all out of bubblegum."
    • It is also a reference to Duke Nukem with the quote "It's time to kick ass and chew bubblegum, and I'm all out of gum."
  • ▶️   "From the frozen loom! Whatever that is." is a reference to the famous quote "For the Frozen Throne!" spoken by numerous characters in WarCraft III.
